divs: Sighting DetailsFrom my back porch and then my front porch, I happenened to look south into the setting sky and observed a pulsating contrail emanting from a horizontal cloud and a few minutes later observed a narrow trail of smoke perpindicular from the contrail. No object was observed. The pulsating contrail reminded me of recent reports of similar sightings.
Summary: Did not see object but observed a pulsating trail emanting from a horizontal cloud
